---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — Evergreen Assessments" description="Our approach to privacy and data handling.">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-neutral">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Effective date:</em> 2025‑10‑01</p>
    <p>We collect minimal information necessary to operate waitlist and contact forms. When you submit a form, we receive the fields you provide (e.g., email, name, message). We do not sell your personal information.</p>
    <h2>Data use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide responses to inquiries and manage early‑access communications.</li>
      <li>Improve the website’s content and measure aggregate interest.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We may use privacy‑respecting analytics (e.g., Plausible) that do not use cookies or collect personal data. See their documentation for details.</p>
    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>Data are transmitted over HTTPS. Netlify hosts static assets and form submissions. Access is restricted to authorized personnel.</p>
    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You may request deletion of your form submission by contacting <a href="mailto:privacy@evergreenassessments.com">privacy@evergreenassessments.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
